---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About - Sunny Compass Labs" description="Learn about the crew behind Sunny Compass Labs and our mission to chart new territory.">
  {/* Page header */}
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-ocean-navy to-cerulean py-24 px-4 text-center">
    <h1 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-7xl text-gold mb-4 animate-sail-in">Our Story</h1>
    <p class="text-sand/80 text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto animate-fade-in-up animate-delay-1">
      Every great voyage starts with a bold crew and a steady compass.
    </p>
  </section>

  {/* Story section */}
  <section class="py-20 px-4 bg-cream">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-8">
      <div class="animate-fade-in-up">
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl text-ocean-navy mb-4">Setting Sail</h2>
        <p class="text-cerulean/80 leading-relaxed text-lg">
          Sunny Compass Labs was born from a simple belief: the most valuable discoveries lie beyond the
          well-charted waters of conventional thinking. Like the great explorers who once navigated by the stars,
          we set our course toward the unknown, driven by curiosity and an unwavering commitment to innovation.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="animate-fade-in-up animate-delay-1">
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl text-ocean-navy mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
        <p class="text-cerulean/80 leading-relaxed text-lg">
          We build tools and products that help people navigate complexity with confidence. In a world overflowing
          with noise, we aim to be the compass that points toward clarity. Our mission is to craft solutions that
          are as reliable as the North Star and as bold as a galleon at full sail.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="animate-fade-in-up animate-delay-2">
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl text-ocean-navy mb-4">The Crew</h2>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border-2 border-sand p-8 text-center">
          <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-gold to-amber rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-ocean-navy" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2" />
              <circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl text-ocean-navy mb-1">Captain Placeholder</h3>
          <p class="text-amber font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Founder &amp; Navigator</p>
          <p class="text-cerulean/70 text-sm max-w-md mx-auto">
            A seasoned explorer with a passion for turning ambitious ideas into reality.
            More details coming soon as our crew assembles.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
